CLI tools for repository management

Usage: rhino-cli [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  repo-governance  Repository governance audits and validators
  md               Markdown validators (links, mermaid, heading-hierarchy, naming, frontmatter,
                   etc.)
  convention       Convention validators (emoji, license)
  harness          Harness (agent binding) validators and generators
  specs            Spec tree validators and contract codegen helpers
  lang             Language-source correctness checks, nested by language
  env              Environment file helpers (init, backup, restore, validate, staged-guard)
  doctor           Check required tool versions are installed and correct
  help             Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -v, --verbose          verbose output with timestamps
  -q, --quiet            quiet mode (errors only)
  -o, --output <OUTPUT>  output format: text, json, markdown [default: text]
      --no-color         disable colored output
      --say <SAY>        echo a message to stdout [default: ""]
  -h, --help             Print help
  -V, --version          Print version

